T1  - The Strategic Role of Information on the Demand Function in an Oligopolistic Market
AU  - Ponssard, Jean-Pierre
Y1  - 1979/03/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.25.3.243
