T1  - Note—On the Complexity of Facilities Layout Problems
AU  - Block, T. E.
Y1  - 1979/03/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.25.3.280
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.25.3.280
